Package: zim
Version: 0.1.0-1
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: git, curl, tar, xz-utils
Maintainer: Ghost Kellz <ghostkellz@example.com>
Description: Zig Infrastructure Manager - All-in-one toolchain and package manager
 ZIM is the next-generation toolchain and package manager for Zig,
 unifying what rustup and cargo do for Rust into one cohesive tool.
 .
 Features:
  * Toolchain management (install, use, pin Zig versions)
  * Dependency management with semantic versioning
  * Content-addressed caching
  * Cross-compilation target support
  * Hash verification and integrity checks
  * Beautiful CLI with comprehensive documentation
Homepage: https://github.com/ghostkellz/zim
